msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Seeker spiritwali u misti"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Curjal, introspektiv, open-minded, u aktar "
"attrattiva għall-għarfien esoteriku. Kunnu jistgħu jkollhom interess żgħir "
"fil-kuntratt tal-meanings meħtieġa jew fil-mustaqbal. Occupazzjonijiet: "
"Ċoach spiritwali, raġenti ta' tarot, astrolajzi, jew individwi magħżula fil-"
"prattiċi tal-New Age. Spektrum ideologiku: Jikkawża lill-ħin spiritwali jew "
"metafisiku. Kunnu jistgħu jħarsu l-għodda bħala mod biex jikkomunika mal-"
"verità profondi jew l-enerġiji universali."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Numaristi u Enthusiasti ta' Gematria"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Analiżi, orientat għad-dettall, u fascinated bil-"
"rapports bejn in-numri u l-lingwa. Kunnu jistgħu jkollhom divertiment fil-"
"interpretazzjoni tal-meanings simboliċi. Occupazzjonijiet: Numaristi "
"freelance, writers fuq l-argijiet esoteriku, jew hobbi u jiskopru numaroli. "
"Spektrum ideologiku: Kunnu jistgħu jkollhom differenti minn dawk li jirranaw"
" numaroli bħala funnu intellettwali għal dawk li jaħsbu l-impatt spiritwal "
"profond."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Istorjani u lingwi"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Scholaru, metodiku, u interessat fil-kontest tal-"
"istorija jew kultur li jwettgħu s-sistemi numarli bħal Abjad. "
"Occupazzjonijiet: Akadmiċi, ricerka, jew studenti li jħarsu l-lingwi ta' "
"l-Mediterranean, l-istorja, jew il-teksti religjonali. Spektrum ideologiku: "
"Kunnu se jikkawża l-għodda minn perspective sekulari u akademiku, iħares "
"lejn il-impatt tal-istorja u linguistika."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Individwi religjonali jew bil-fiduċja"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Devut, riflessiv, u seħba li jikkonnettaw l-fiduċja "
"tagħhom. Kunnu jistgħu jżżomm il-għodda biex jitqawdru l-teksti religjonali "
"jew il-messaggi divini. Occupazzjonijiet: Scholaru religjovi, imams, "
"priests, jew laypeople li jkollhom interess fuq l-tradizzjonijiet misti tal-"
"fiduċja. Spektrum ideologiku: Kunnu se jkollu worldview tradizzjonali jew "
"konservattiv, u jħareġ l-għodda biex jiżviluppa l-impatt spiritwali."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Auturi u Artisti"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Kreattiv, imġinattiv, u attrattiva għal konċetti "
"simboliċi u abstratti. Kunnu jistgħu jħarsu l-għodda għall-inspirazzjoni jew"
" biex jżid layers ta' meanig għat-tkabbir tagħhom. Occupazzjonijiet: Auturi,"
" poeti, artisti visivi, jew musikanti. Spektrum ideologiku: Kunnu jistgħu "
"jkollhom differenzi bejn kreattivi sekulari u dawk li għandhom tendenza "
"spiritwal jew misti."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Enthusiasti ta' Puzzle u Riddles"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Għażiż, intellettwali, u jkollhom divertiment fil-"
"soluzzjoni ta' problemi komplessi jew l-interpretazzjoni ta' patterns. "
"Occupazzjonijiet: Hobbyists, puzzle designers, jew edukaturi. Spektrum "
"ideologiku: Kunnu se jagħmlu l-għodda bħala forma ta' entertainment jew "
"liżzi ta' mental, bl-iktar mal-attacc ideologiku."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Teoristi ta' Kkonspirazzjoni u Ħsieb alternattiv"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Traits tal-Personalità: Skeptiku minn narattivi mainstream, attrattiva "
"għall-kuntratt ta' verità meħtieġa u patterns fil-sistemi. Occupazzjonijiet:"
" Ricerki indipendenti, bloggers, jew activist. Spektrum ideologiku: Kunnu "
"jista' jkollhom worldview radikali jew unconventional, u jħareġ il-għodda "
"biex issupporta l-ideat alternattivi."

